{"tid":2447281,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"沙塵暴來襲｜北京空氣污染爆錶 逾400航班取消 12省巿現黃沙","createTime":"2021-03-15T05:51:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T10:18:05.000Z","uid":75969,"like":69,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":82,"replies":[{"pid":"24b8f9811470c3f04cc812c07e8bbec3e11dfff3","tid":2447281,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T05:51:07.000Z","msg":"內地北方地區今年首次遭到大範圍的沙塵暴吹襲，多個省巿早上都呈現一片灰黃。中央氣象台預警，新疆、內蒙古等12省市今日（15日）將出現明顯的沙塵天氣，部份地區會遭遇近10年強度最強、範圍最廣的沙塵暴。在北京，大部份地區能見度小於1公里，過百班航機要取消，當局要呼籲教育機構停止戶外活動。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/KBQTzVVFzuxzqaiW2Wor5DAuV-M=/802x391/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/V6SSH5SILBFZZPPHRG3R5GLMFI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FKBQTzVVFzuxzqaiW2Wor5DAuV-M%3D%2F802x391%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FV6SSH5SILBFZZPPHRG3R5GLMFI.jpg&h=1aa4228e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地媒體的片段顯示，北京一早被沙塵籠罩，巿內一片昏黃，街上的民眾都紛紛戴上口罩。早上7時25分，北京市氣象局發佈沙塵暴預警信號，請各區教委、直屬學校、中等職業學校及校外教育機構暫停戶外活動並做好健康防護。截至早上9時，北京首都國際機場和大興國際機場，已經有超過400班航機被取消。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/VmXXhplQ6AGPflB7Q9Lcbbk3b7Q=/802x438/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WN5SJARWOVDVVEFGUWZNDOGO6M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVmXXhplQ6AGPflB7Q9Lcbbk3b7Q%3D%2F802x438%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWN5SJARWOVDVVEFGUWZNDOGO6M.jpg&h=31387ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n北京環境監測網站顯示，今日中午，北京市空氣品質指數為500，為指數最高水平，污染級別為6級，達嚴重污染水平。中央氣象台隨後升級發佈沙塵暴黃色預警信號，指空氣中首要污染物為PM10，早上8時PM10全市平均達到1000微克每立方米以上，巿內大部份地區能見度小於1公里，預料沙塵暴天氣會持續一整天。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/VQ4SqJPKPRURbOiY18kXmFn4-q4=/802x908/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RIQZEP3CVNAB3MCFU3XVKN6LEY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVQ4SqJPKPRURbOiY18kXmFn4-q4%3D%2F802x908%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRIQZEP3CVNAB3MCFU3XVKN6LEY.jpg&h=5d89fbdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中央氣象台發佈消息指﹐昨日（14日）至今晨，受冷空氣影響，預計新疆、內蒙古、甘肅、寧夏、陝西、山西、河北、北京、天津、黑龍江、吉林、遼寧等12省市將出現明顯的沙塵天氣，部份地區有沙塵暴，經估算，衞星顯示的沙塵暴面積約為46.6萬平方公里，是近10年內地遭遇強度最強、影響範圍最廣的一次沙塵暴天氣。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210315/2A4HQI4TCRDAZPBGPHYPRX3SOY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210315%2F2A4HQI4TCRDAZPBGPHYPRX3SOY%2F&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDkx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=4072f6cf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210315%2F2A4HQI4TCRDAZPBGPHYPRX3SOY%2F&h=5123ae5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210315/2A4HQI4TCRDAZPBGPHYPRX3SOY/</a>"},{"pid":"d43a4ee67e1899b664bae152f0833198b3908d26","tid":2447281,"uid":60924,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T05:52:02.000Z","msg":"好黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2075dcdd862e461e53ad66c729e26faf671aa001","tid":2447281,"uid":318414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T05:53:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03ac89ba3d4c967cfc132657a903f1267af216af","tid":2447281,"uid":343327,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T05:54:36.000Z","msg":"深黃<img src=\"/asse